														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-806158">
									

<p>It *has* to be 914, built through 217…which, in retrospect…is so *obvious*. How could I not have noticed it before? Amazing….</p>
<p>Never thought that the gears and cogs of 217-infectees would maintain their skills, even a little bit…but they <em>must</em> if they retain memories and habits…if you took bits and pieces from everybody, pieced them together…and threw in that little dash of obsession and burning desire to change the world that seems to cause the spontaneous generation of SCPs…</p>
<p>…This could mean that 882 is also directly connected to 217, either as progenitor or descendant. Hmmm…</p>

